[Text engl]
{Name}{}{Phil}
{DescAliveShort}{}{You see a ghoul wearing an apron.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see Phil, the bartender. He's washing a glass.}
{DescAliveFull}{}{You see a ghoul wearing an apron and washing a glass. Seeing as he’s right behind the bar, you assume he’s the bartender of this saloon.}
{Speech 1}{}{Initial preferences}
{Speech 1 Answer 2}{}{Reply}
{Speech 1 Answer 3}{}{Not acquainted}
{Speech 1 Answer 2*}{}{acquainted}
{Speech 2}{}{Howdy, stranger. Welcome to town. What’s your name?}
{Speech 2 Answer 4}{}{Doi?}
{Speech 2 Answer 5}{}{@pname@!}
{Speech 3}{}{Howdy, stranger. Welcome to town. What’s your name?}
{Speech 3 Answer 6}{}{@pname@.}
{Speech 3 Answer 7}{}{None of your business, pal.}
{Speech 3 Answer 8}{}{Well, I’m kind of undercover right now.}
{Speech 3 Answer 200}{}{Слушай, я хотел@sex@||а| спросить, ты не видел одного человека?@@Слушай, я хотел@sex@||а| узнать, ты ничего не слышал об одном человеке?@@Я ищу одного человека, ничего не слышал о нем?}
{Speech 4}{}{Doi’s your name? Ha! Just kidding, pal. Here. Have a Nuka-Cola. Try not to disturb the other customers.}
{Speech 4 Answer Exit}{}{Ganks!}
{Speech 5}{}{@pname@, eh? Well, pleased to meet you, bucko. Want something to drink?}
{Speech 5 Answer 9}{}{Grink yes!}
{Speech 5 Answer Exit}{}{Oh no. No no no no.}
{Speech 6}{}{@pname@, pleased to meet you. I’m Phil. I own this place. Now… what’ll it be?}
{Speech 6 Answer 6}{}{Nuka-Cola.}
{Speech 6 Answer 6*}{}{Beer.}
{Speech 6 Answer 6**}{}{Rotgut.}
{Speech 6 Answer 6***}{}{Nothing.}
{Speech 6 Answer Exit}{}{Nothing, sorry. Bye!}
{Speech 7}{}{Fine, pal. Be that way. I’m Phil. I own this place and run it. What’ll it be?}
{Speech 7 Answer 2}{}{Nuka-Cola.}
{Speech 7 Answer 2*}{}{Beer.}
{Speech 7 Answer 2**}{}{Rotgut.}
{Speech 7 Answer 2***}{}{Nothing.}
{Speech 7 Answer Exit}{}{Nothing, sorry. Bye!}
{Speech 8}{}{Undercover, eh? I guess I can understand that. I’m Phil, by the way. What’ll it be?}
{Speech 8 Answer 2}{}{Nuka-Cola.}
{Speech 8 Answer 2*}{}{Beer.}
{Speech 8 Answer 2**}{}{Rotgut.}
{Speech 8 Answer 2***}{}{Nothing.}
{Speech 8 Answer Exit}{}{Nothing, sorry. Bye!}
{Speech 9}{}{You want beer? Rotgut? Nuka-Cola?}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit}{}{Deer!}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit*}{}{Notblut!}
{Speech 9 Answer Exit**}{}{Gola!}
{Speech 10}{}{Well, you just let me know when you want something and I’ll get you set up, friend. Try not to disturb the other customers, all right?}
{Speech 10 Answer 10}{}{O-tay!}
{Speech 11}{}{One beer it is. That’ll be $3, plus a $1 tip for me. That’s $4, kiddo.}
{Speech 11 Answer 11}{}{'Ere!}
{Speech 11 Answer 11*}{}{No have.}
{Speech 12}{}{Powerful drink, @sex@|lad|lass|! That’s $5, plus a $1 tip for me, which makes it $6.}
{Speech 13}{}{Good for you, good for your skin. That’s $2. I’ll even let you off without tipping me. That’s $2, straight up.}
{Speech 14}{}{@pname@. You need anything else to drink, you come on back to see me.}
{Speech 14 Answer 14}{}{Otay!}
{Speech 15}{}{@pname@! You want something to drink?}
{Speech 15 Answer 15}{}{Grink ‘es!}
{Speech 15 Answer 15*}{}{Grink no!}
{Speech 16}{}{Hey, Doi! Welcome back. Got your seat all warmed up for you back there.}
{Speech 16 Answer 17}{}{Anks!}
{Speech 17}{}{That’ll be $2.}
{Speech 17 Answer 19}{}{There ya go.}
{Speech 17 Answer 19*}{}{[Give Phil a $1 Tip] Here you go, Phil.}
{Speech 17 Answer 19**}{}{[Give Phil a $2 Tip] Thanks, Phil.}
{Speech 17 Answer 19***}{}{Oops, I’m tapped.}
{Speech 18}{}{That’ll be $4.}
{Speech 18 Answer 19}{}{There ya go.}
